2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep learning based methods for fault detection, which falls under the purview of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning based methods for fault detection, which falls under the purview of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses a Generative Adversarial Network based autoencoder, which falls under the purview of neural computing. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering): Although not the primary focus of the paper, the proposed method can have applications in software engineering for fault detection in closed loop systems.
